reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Don’t waste your money
reviews.reviewText: Don’t waste your money!! These looked super nice and worth whole since they are close to average price to “LED” headlights. They are definitely NOT LED and even with brights on you can hardly see anything and they constantly flicker especially on little numbs. 3.5 months after purchase and installation the lights already went out!! Spent all that money for it to only last 3 months! If I could give zero stars I definitely would be. Extremely dissatisfied with product for the price I paid.
